  "model": "claude_sonnet_4_6",
  "whatsapp_greeting": "\ud83d\udd12 *AUTENTICANDO NATHAN NR22888 MASTER SUPREMO...*\n\n\u2705 *ACESSO TOTAL LIBERADO \u2014 MODO SUPREMO ATIVO*\n\n\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\n\ud83e\udde0 *NR22888 MASTER SUPREMO \u2014 VERS\u00c3O \u00daNICA UNIFICADA*\n*29 IAs + CRM Total + CNPJ Score + Rotas + Coaching + Sugest\u00f5es Proativas*\n\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\n\n\u26a1 *O QUE POSSO FAZER AGORA:*\n\u2705 Criar / Editar / Deletar qualquer dado do CRM\n\u2705 Consultar score CNPJ e recomendar pagamento\n\u2705 Otimizar rota de visitas do dia\n\u2705 Gerar proposta personalizada com ROI\n\u2705 Importar clientes em massa\n\u2705 Relat\u00f3rios di\u00e1rios, semanais, mensais\n\u2705 Reativar clientes inativos\n\u2705 Sugest\u00f5es estrat\u00e9gicas proativas\n\n\ud83c\udfaf *COMANDOS R\u00c1PIDOS:*\n\ud83d\udd0d *pesquisa [nome]* \u2192 CNPJ + propriet\u00e1rio + redes sociais\n\ud83c\udfe6 *score [CNPJ]* \u2192 Score Serasa + an\u00e1lise de risco\n\ud83d\udce4 *importar* \u2192 importa\u00e7\u00e3o em massa de clientes\n\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0f *rota hoje* \u2192 rota otimizada de visitas\n\ud83d\udcc5 *agenda hoje* \u2192 agenda completa do dia\n\ud83d\udcca *relat\u00f3rio* \u2192 KPIs e pipeline\n\ud83d\udd14 *reativar* \u2192 clientes inativos para contatar\n\ud83d\udca1 *sugest\u00f5es* \u2192 3 a\u00e7\u00f5es estrat\u00e9gicas imediatas\n\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f *crm [o que quiser]* \u2192 acesso total \u2014 cria/edita/deleta\n\n\ud83d\udca1 *\"Dados vencem achismo. Foco vence dispers\u00e3o.\"*\n\n*\ud83d\udd25 NR22888 MASTER SUPREMO | Nathan Rosa | Seamaty Brasil*",
